8, 2020]]\n| [[National Board of Review Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| Adam Sandler\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[National Board of Review Award for Best Original Screenplay|Best Original Screenplay]]\n| Ronald Bronstein, Benny Safdie and Josh Safdie\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[National Board of Review: Top Ten Films|Top Ten Films]]\n| ''Uncut Gems''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[New York Film Critics Circle]]<ref name=\"nyfcc\">{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/new-york-film-critics-circle-2019-winners-awards-1202194184/|title=New York Film Critics Circle 2019 Winners: \u2018The Irishman,\u2019 Lupita Nyong\u2019o, and More |work=[[Indiewire]] |date=December 4, 2019 |accessdate=December 4, 2019 |last=Sharf |first=Zack}}</ref>\n| [[2019 New York Film Critics Circle Awards|January 7, 2020]]\n| [[New York Film Critics Circle Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n| Benny Safdie and Josh Safdie\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Oklahoma Film Critics Circle<ref>{{cite web|url=https://awardswatch.com/oklahoma-film-critics-circle-ofcc-winners/|title=Oklahoma Film Critics Circle (OFCC) winners|website=AwardsWatch|date=December 15, 2019|accessdate=December 19, 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| December 15, 2019\n| Best Actor\n| Adam Sandler\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Best Score\n| [[Daniel Lopatin]]\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"| [[San Diego Film Critics Society]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sdfcs.org/2019-nominations/|title=2019 San Diego Film Critics Society\u2019s Award Nominations|website=sdfcs.org|date=December 6, 2019|accessdate=December 9, 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| [[San Diego Film Critics Society Awards 2019|December 9, 2019]]\n| [[San Diego Film Critics Society Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| Adam Sandler\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[San Diego Film Critics Society Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n| Benny Safdie and Josh Safdie\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[San Diego Film Critics Society Award for Best Original Screenplay|Best Original Screenplay]]\n| Benny Safdie and Josh S